description: Bathed in natural light, this gated contemporary captures the essence of California living with its seamless indoor/outdoor design and serene garden setting. The expansive living room flows to an inviting cabana dining space perfect for year-round entertaining under the Beverly Hills sky.  A sleek European kitchen opens to the formal dining room and out to a lush meditation and flower garden that wraps the property in color and calm. The oversized primary suite offers dual spa-inspired bathrooms, a generous custom closet, and a private terrace with treetop views. A bright secondary suite provides the perfect complement for family or guests. Moments from the iconic Beverly Hills Hotel and the heart of the city, this rare retreat embodies timeless California style in one of the world's most celebrated neighborhoods.
